	<a href="http://www.devhood.com/tools/tool_details.aspx?tool_id=261">XMLNotePad 1.0</a>.&nbsp; Where Microsoft's XML  Notepad 1.0 can be found, according to MSDN!<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106101195422769595">Friday, August 15, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
