	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106101166769577197">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/msdnmag/issues/01/09/web/default.aspx">Web Q&A: XPath, XML Notepad, Data Islands, Case Sensitivity, XSL, and More -- MSDN Magazine, September 2001</a>.&nbsp; This page confirms that the XML Notepad is not available from Microsoft "right now."<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106101166769577197">Friday, August 15, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
