	<a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/downloads/list/xmlgeneral.asp">Downloads</a>.&nbsp; Here are the basic core tools that Microsoft provides for processing XML, XSL/XSLT, etc.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106101147992889133">Friday, August 15, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
