	<a href="http://www7b.software.ibm.com/dmdd/library/samples/videocentral/videocentral.html">IBM Video Central for e-business tutorial</a>.&nbsp; This is a video (rental) system developed as a Web Services demonstration and tutorial.&nbsp; It features DB2 and it works through the developer trails, the application, and the steps taken to create and establish the services.<br>
